Installation procedure for peerlist:

1.) untar

  $ tar jxfv peerlist-latest.tar.bz2

2.) change directory

  $ cd peerlist-<version>/

2.) configure

  $ less MODULE-OPTIONS
  $ vi config.inc.php

3.) set permissions

  $ chmod 777 tmp/


all done.

Please check the templates in the templates/ dir for alterations. A bit of trial-and-error should help you there.

